{"tid":469862,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"簡體字真係好核突","createTime":"2017-11-15T17:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T08:43:55.000Z","uid":5077,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ed03ef3c19373b807614ae8bcc7e92330045fc44","tid":469862,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"唔係話有偏見，<br />\n但係簡體字根本無嗰種字型美，欠缺形神，<br />\n好核突"},{"pid":"cbe36fe77763512c70adc42ad041b34d05f1f3f4","tid":469862,"uid":2155,"like":2,"dislike":72,"score":-70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:50:25.000Z","msg":"对呀"},{"pid":"f28620b02e1c7e9e0d6436d351bda33b02c2278b","tid":469862,"uid":13554,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"唔知點解<br />\n明明日文用啲漢字都係簡體 但又唔覺得有問題<br />\n蝗國成堆簡體彈出黎 又會覺得柒到仆街"},{"pid":"115e9b4d29c0b4d815807e2c066be2e526fae7da","tid":469862,"uid":10981,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>对呀</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"850695dbffac0ec1236d89239a05bf9cc2391aa4","tid":469862,"uid":23914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"你個媽係女人"},{"pid":"14dd079e0ad2f43b33c780ec412cf1416f73ea1e","tid":469862,"uid":157411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 蝦翁炒蛋"},{"pid":"e55bcf9f7a93b9a0d4dcaa5c2887b5c621563005","tid":469862,"uid":152376,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:16:43.000Z","msg":"繁體字先喺真正嘅中文"},{"pid":"cd1735b4b0bae18a888f461106cbe2a670fec4fe","tid":469862,"uid":146917,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"都是中文，不用分得这么ching"},{"pid":"abb70468025e0991ebd1284bd6cedc773f1e108c","tid":469862,"uid":12404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解<br />\n明明日文用啲漢字都係簡體 但又唔覺得有問題<br />\n蝗國成堆簡體彈出黎 又會覺得柒到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和製漢字簡化得嚟應該有嘢嘅地方都會有返嘢<br />\n<br />\n例如 「广」 「広」"},{"pid":"8965fefbd2924dcb5e57d4dae972af8cc1a332c9","tid":469862,"uid":80176,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解<br />\n明明日文用啲漢字都係簡體 但又唔覺得有問題<br />\n蝗國成堆簡體彈出黎 又會覺得柒到仆街</blockquote><br />\n因為你盲崇日"},{"pid":"00631b9afa57fd0aac4bcb706b1bcf2c6022c397","tid":469862,"uid":12404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解<br />\n明明日文用啲漢字都係簡體 但又唔覺得有問題<br />\n蝗國成堆簡體彈出黎 又會覺得柒到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和製漢字簡化得嚟應該有嘢嘅地方都會有返嘢<br />\n<br />\n例如 「广」 「広」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那字 連一啲好簡單號部首都簡化咗<br />\n<br />\n例如 金/言 字旁<br />\n<br />\n正如一個人冇咗眼耳口鼻是但一樣，嗰個人望落就會好怪雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5044e58916ffad5aedf81e7584d16757d5b164c","tid":469862,"uid":31522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7298a592e2e8575043af4ce077edbe878b8a6571","tid":469862,"uid":12404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解<br />\n明明日文用啲漢字都係簡體 但又唔覺得有問題<br />\n蝗國成堆簡體彈出黎 又會覺得柒到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和製漢字簡化得嚟應該有嘢嘅地方都會有返嘢<br />\n<br />\n例如 「广」 「広」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那字 連一啲好簡單號部首都簡化咗<br />\n<br />\n例如 金/言 字旁<br />\n<br />\n正如一個人冇咗眼耳口鼻是但一樣，嗰個人望落就會好怪雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再舉多一個例<br />\n<br />\n支那：「经」 日本：「経」<br />\n<br />\n先唔講糹嗰三點根本冇簡化嘅必要<br />\n<br />\nス 同 又  / エ 同 土 筆劃根本係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要支那隻字反而係由假名組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日文個 経 字一睇明顯飽滿好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfb9b1467f7db3b212889db5bc1ccfb0b345f46","tid":469862,"uid":145019,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:36:22.000Z","msg":"其實有樣野唔明<br />\n明明係因為當時支那多文盲所以先有殘體字<br />\n但到而家,做野果班都算,連讀書,教中文果班人都係到用殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書人走去用埋d文盲用既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上由細到大學寫字都係學繁體字,但而家唔識寫殘體字反而比人當怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：堅持寫繁體字,完全唔識寫殘體字"},{"pid":"49141110e1857c4725a73f6871156edd22c3dfa2","tid":469862,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:37:46.000Z","msg":"聽聞而家支那都學繁體字"},{"pid":"b1caa6cfd62826dd5f5dc4f5c6ef6b0e06a3bd54","tid":469862,"uid":65144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:38:25.000Z","msg":"毛筆用繁體字真係好有氣勢"},{"pid":"e9657eba5ac2032157179f9893a46b881439df79","tid":469862,"uid":154800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:24:21.000Z","msg":"簡體字真係核突到無文化ge人先寫得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f15fe1fa7d610dc998ecdceeea693f96c3a6781","tid":469862,"uid":8984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:27:17.000Z","msg":"見親一堆殘體字都頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e318afd4b4d024056f3d3388391370f0ac53d2","tid":469862,"uid":76883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T22:54:49.000Z","msg":"殘體識睇唔識寫 但會睇得好慢<br />\n好多時見到一大篇殘體會睇都唔睇 感覺睇完會降低我中文程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3871e225b9eb63fe41e5c9e06730376d3ed9a4","tid":469862,"uid":51924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T23:09:46.000Z","msg":"比文盲用既係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"c5134c470c64cee096e640eb7927797c4d21a960","tid":469862,"uid":5077